<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { color: #ff6b00; font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .otp-container { background: #f5f5f5; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; text-align: center; margin: 20px 0; }
        .otp-code { font-size: 28px; letter-spacing: 3px; color: #ff6b00; font-weight: bold; }
        .footer { margin-top: 30px; font-size: 12px; color: #777; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">Delivery Verification</div>
    
    <p>Hello {{username}},</p>
    
    <p>Your delivery for order #{{orderId}} is almost complete. Please provide the following OTP code to the delivery person to verify the delivery:</p>
    
    <div class="otp-container">
        <div class="otp-code">{{otp}}</div>
        <div>(This code is valid for 10 minutes)</div>
    </div>
    
    <p>If you didn't request this delivery, please contact our support team immediately.</p>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>Best regards,</p>
        <p>Grocejet Delivery Team</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>